::Zardus/DevilDuer/Perndabot/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Zardus and co. land in the Alliance base, entering it.

"Put those two in the brig," Zardus says to Perndabot, refferring to the 
maximal prisoners and handing him Iron Raptor. Perndabot nods, setting off 
toward the brig with a maximal slung over his shoulder. Zardus sets off 
toward the bridge as DevilDuer, Reptilica, and Bloodystrike head for the CR 
chamber.
